He was a lovely fella.

33:30.884 --> 33:32.886
Funny, kind...

33:33.512 --> 33:35.073
- Hung like a...
- Please.

33:35.097 --> 33:37.474
Too much information.

33:38.017 --> 33:40.602
I can't believe you're
laughing about him, poor man.

33:41.270 --> 33:44.082
Gerald clocked-off with a
smile on his face, Sandra.

33:44.106 --> 33:45.983
That's all any of
us can hope for.

33:47.401 --> 33:49.486
Aren't you scared of dying?

33:50.863 --> 33:52.448
What's there to
be frightened of?

33:53.699 --> 33:54.742
Well, the fact that...

33:55.909 --> 33:56.952
That that's it.

33:58.078 --> 33:59.496
As Mark twain said,

