39:58.772 --> 40:01.918
Okay, stop, stop, stop!
This really is a mash-up.

40:01.942 --> 40:04.545
All right, look, don't
get disheartened.

40:04.569 --> 40:06.047
We will get there.

40:06.071 --> 40:07.882
Yeah, if I don't have
a coronary first.

40:07.906 --> 40:12.303
But you must practise these steps at home.
It's the only way we're gonna remember.

40:12.327 --> 40:14.472
I can't even remember
my own name.

40:14.496 --> 40:16.349
Okay, are we ready to go again?

40:16.373 --> 40:17.725
- Yes.
- Yeah.

40:17.749 --> 40:19.334
Okay. Zach, music.

40:26.883 --> 40:29.404
What the hell have you done?

40:29.428 --> 40:30.470
Tidied up.

40:31.596 --> 40:34.283
Well, how am I supposed
to find anything now?

40:34.307 --> 40:35.392
