56:24.965 --> 56:26.342
It's gone viral.

56:27.468 --> 56:29.738
Tsk, she looks ridiculous.

56:29.762 --> 56:32.139
She's had her hair done.
It's knocked years off her.

56:34.141 --> 56:36.102
- Ooh!
- Sorry. Foot slipped.

