01:41:45.141 --> 01:41:49.646
Do you remember that
time in claridge's when,

01:41:50.605 --> 01:41:52.440
when we told her to
get the sommelier,

01:41:53.108 --> 01:41:55.610
and she tried to order
two bottles of it?

